OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778418667
OL,3,CLondon demonstrators call for
OL,4,Cabolition of the monarchy
OL,6,FAround 100 demonstrators have gathered
OL,7,Fin central London to call for the
OL,8,Fabolition of the monarchy.
OL,10,FThe anti-monarchy pressure group
OL,11,FRepublic organised the march from
OL,12,FTrafalgar Square to Buckingham Palace.
OL,14,FWriter Otto English took to the stage
OL,15,Fin Trafalgar Square and claimed the
OL,16,Flocal elections showed that democracy
OL,17,Fis broken. He said:
OL,19,F"Democracy is broken, the local
OL,20,Felections showed us that.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778418667
OL,3,CLondon demonstrators call for
OL,4,Cabolition of the monarchy
OL,6,F"I think all the elections we have had
OL,7,Frecently have shown us that.
OL,9,F"It is broken to such an extent that
OL,10,Fit needs fixing and that goes right to
OL,11,Fthe top.
OL,13,F"That in a nutshell is why I am a
OL,14,Frepublican."
OL,16,FDemonstrators wore t-shirts and held
OL,17,Fsigns which read "abolish the
OL,18,Fmonarchy" and "not my King".
OL,20,FElizabeth McIntyre, a member of the
OL,21,Fgroup from London, said:
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@LO]yD@ROUzD@IO]zD@OOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778418667
OL,3,CLondon demonstrators call for
OL,4,Cabolition of the monarchy
OL,6,F"I really object to the class system
OL,7,Fin this country.
OL,9,F"I think it creates a hierarchy which
OL,10,Fis absolutely unacceptable.
OL,12,F"At the top of that hierarchy is an
OL,13,Funelected monarchy, which means that
OL,14,Ffrom top to bottom there is
OL,15,Finequality, and this has to go."
OL,17,FGraham Smith, leader of Republic,
OL,18,Fclaimed the movement is growing,
OL,19,Fespecially after the death of Queen
OL,20,FElizabeth II. He said:
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778418667
OL,3,CLondon demonstrators call for
OL,4,Cabolition of the monarchy
OL,6,F"We want everybody outside the palace
OL,7,Fmaking a statement.
OL,9,F"It is about showing that we are
OL,10,Fgrowing and there is a mood change.
OL,11,FTwenty years ago this wasn't happening
OL,12,Fat all, there is a big change in
OL,13,Fpublic mood.
OL,15,F"In 2022 we could not have even
OL,16,Fthought of doing something like this.
OL,17,FIt wasn't on the cards, we didn't have
OL,18,Fthe staff or the money, and now this
OL,19,Fis third event we have done.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778418667
OL,3,CLondon demonstrators call for
OL,4,Cabolition of the monarchy
OL,6,F"We have an impressive list of people
OL,7,Fcoming along, people are seeing us and
OL,8,Funderstanding who we are, and they are
OL,9,Flistening to what we are saying, and
OL,10,Fthey want to be a part of it.
OL,12,F"The death of the Queen and the
OL,13,Fcoronation completely changed
OL,14,Feverything for us.
OL,16,F"We suddenly grew, we suddenly went
OL,17,Ffrom one member of staff to loads of
OL,18,Fstaff."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
